songs.title: The field
songs.lyrics: Back den all these bitches didn't want me, now when they see me they be actin like they know me, young savage can't starve im gone eat, ion even know what happened to the old me, niggas talking shit but they dont want no beef, choppa hit him leave his ass on the slow leaf, no limit all these opp niggas want piece, and you know i got the squad like kobe, foreal doe, they used to call me a weirdo, but all of a sudden im all these niggas heroes, takin off but im bout to switch gears doe, how the fuck you trappin hard and you still broke? Bad bitch with a bad lil walk, im a bag that bitch ian even gotta talk, just spent 10k and i forgot what I bought, i be flexin on haters give a fuck what you thought, money on his head tryin not to get bought, my youngins doing hits tryin not to get caught, trappin all day with da r and da sault, 30's in the cut tryin not to get offed, real shit thats the life of a young nigga, riddin round still gotta keep the guns wit us, a lot of hatin ass niggas and these groupie ass bitches, ian trippin cause i know this shit come with it
